    {
      "lineNumber": 1,
      "text": "Director of Special Investigations",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 2,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 3,
      "text": "\"As a civilian body of investigators, we hope",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 4,
      "text": "to unravel the snarled mess that shrouds the U.F.O.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 5,
      "text": "question, and with the help of the newspapers and",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 6,
      "text": "the public, where can we fail?",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 7,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 8,
      "text": "\"We will be grateful if you will publish the",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9,
      "text": "enclosed appeal on the front page of your newspaper,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 10,
      "text": "in a conspicuous enough manner that no one will fail",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 11,
      "text": "- to notice it. It is the public we must depend upon",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12,
      "text": "to get thoroughly organized, and with this co-operation",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 13,
      "text": "we are certain that we can find the answer to the",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 14,
      "text": "riddle of the 'Flying Saucers.'",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 15,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 16,
      "text": "\"If a Filter Center has been established in your",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 17,
      "text": "state or province, this form letter will carry its",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 18,
      "text": "address which should replace the headquarters address",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "text": "given on the enclosed 'Public Notice.' If no such",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "text": "filter center address is given, then the original",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "text": "headquarters address should be used.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "text": "\"We wish to thank you for any assistance you may",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "text": "be able to give us in this respect. Later established",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
